  "texts": [
    "To address this issue, SRDDGAN is proposed.",
    "This method utilizes complex multimodal distributions to model each denoising step, allowing for more giant denoising strides.",
    "To alleviate the ill-posedness of super-resolution, latent variable Z is introduced to diversify the predictions of SR.",
    "Furthermore, to exploit the adequate information on Low-Resolution (LR) efficiently, a custom LR encoder module is employed to constrain the solution space of HR using a simple conditional generation approach.",
    "Finally, style and content loss functions are combined to recover some high-frequency details."
